  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Effects of a Low Free Sugar Diet in Patients With Nonalcoholic Fatty Liver Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Effects of a Low Free Sugar Diet on Lipid Profile, Glycemic Indices, Liver Enzymes, Inflammatory Factors and Hepatic Steatosis and Fibrosis in Patients With Nonalcoholic Fatty Liver Disease</official_title>
